            <TextView
                style="@style/textinfo"
                android:text="To learn about the habits of birds, all you need to do is pay attention and observe them. " />

            <TextView
                style="@style/textinfo"
                android:text="For example, red-billed Quelea are often found in large flocks, Brown-snake Eagles tend to sit on top of dead trees in plain sight, and Burchell's Coucals often run around inside bushes. " />

            <TextView
                style="@style/textinfo"
                android:text="By learning these habits, you can gain additional information that can be useful in identifying birds." />


